<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Account Deletion Request Received</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
<style>
    body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #f4f4f4;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
}
.container-sec {
  background-color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-top: 30px;
  box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  max-width: 600px;
}
.otp-code {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: bold;
  background-color: #f8f9fa;
  padding: 15px;
  text-align: center;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px dashed #007bff;
  color: #007bff;
}
.footer-text {
  color: #6c757d;
  font-size: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 20px;
}
.footer-text a {
  color: #007bff;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.welcome-section {
  background: #144fa9db;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 20px;
  margin: 20px 0px;
}
.welcome-text {
  font-family: monospace;
}
.app-name {
  font-size: 30px;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin: 7px 0px;
}
.verify-text {
  margin-top: 25px;
  font-size: 25px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}
i.fas.fa-envelope-open {
  font-size: 35px !important;
  color: #ffffff;
}

</style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container-sec">
    <div class="text-center" style="text-align: center";>
      <div class="welcome-section">
        <div class="app-name">
          --- SMMBIDMEDIA ---
        </div>
        <div class="welcome-text">
          Security Update!
        </div>

        <div class="verify-text">
          Account Deletion Request Received
        </div>
        <div class="email-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope-open"></i>
        </div>

      </div>
      <h2>Hello, <%= name %></h2>
      <p>We have received your request to delete your account. 
        Your request is currently under review and is pending approval by our customer support team.</p>
        <p>Once your request has been reviewed and approved, we will notify you, and the account deletion process will proceed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-text">
      <p>If you have any questions or wish to cancel your request, please contact our support team within the next 48 hours.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>The <%= appName %> Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>